# Astro Component Standards

## 🎯 When to Use Astro vs Svelte

**Use Astro components when:**
- No JavaScript interactivity is needed (static/presentational components)
- Component is purely server-rendered with no client-side state
- Zero JavaScript bundle size is desired
- Simple data display or layout structure

**Use Svelte components when:**
- JavaScript interactivity is required (event handlers, state management, reactivity)
- Client-side state or reactivity is needed (`$state`, `$derived`, `$effect`)
- Component needs to respond to user interactions
- Dynamic behavior or animations are required

**Rule of thumb:** If it doesn't need JavaScript, use Astro. If it needs JavaScript, use Svelte.

---

## 📁 File Structure

### Astro Component Template
```astro
---
// apps/seo/ui/src/components/component-name.astro
// 1. Imports (Astro, components, types, utilities)
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SomeComponent from '../features/feature-name/components/some-component.svelte';

// 2. TypeScript interfaces/types (if needed)
interface ComponentProps {
  title: string;
  optional?: boolean;
}

// 3. Props destructuring
const { title, optional = false }: ComponentProps = Astro.props;

// 4. Data fetching/computation (if needed)
const data = await fetchData();
---

<!-- 5. HTML template -->
<Layout>
  <main>
    <h1>{title}</h1>
    <SomeComponent client:load />
  </main>
</Layout>

<!-- 6. Scoped styles (if needed) -->
<style>
  main {
    padding: 1rem;
  }
</style>
```

### Component Organization
```
src/
├── layouts/           # Page layouts (Layout.astro, etc.)
├── pages/            # Route pages (index.astro, about.astro)
├── components/       # Shared Astro components
│   └── component-name/
│       ├── component-name.astro
│       └── index.ts
└── features/         # Feature-based modules (same as React/Svelte)
    └── [feature-name]/
        ├── components/    # Svelte components
        │   └── component-name/
        │       ├── component-name.svelte
        │       ├── component-name.module.scss (optional)
        │       └── index.ts
        ├── containers/    # Svelte containers
        │   └── container-name/
        │       ├── container-name.svelte
        │       └── index.ts
        └── *.astro        # Astro wrappers/integrations
```

