## 📐 Layout Patterns

### Page Layout Structure
```astro
---
// src/layouts/Layout.astro
import HeaderContainer from '../features/header/containers/header-container.svelte';
import FooterWrapper from '../components/FooterWrapper.astro';
import '../styles/globals.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <title>{Astro.props.title || 'Default Title'}</title>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <HeaderContainer client:load />
    <div class="flex-1">
      <slot />
    </div>
    <FooterWrapper />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  html,
  body {
    margin: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }
</style>
```

### Page Structure
```astro
---
// src/pages/index.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <!-- Page content -->
  </main>
</Layout>
```

