## 🎨 Styling Guidelines

### TailwindCSS (Preferred)
- **Use Tailwind classes** for all styling
- **Prefer utility classes** over custom CSS
- **Use arbitrary values** when needed: `bg-[#606581]`, `rounded-[15px]`

```astro
<div class="max-w-[930px] mx-auto px-10 mb-5 flex flex-col gap-6 md:flex-row md:gap-[80px]">
  <!-- Content -->
</div>
```

### Scoped Styles (When Needed)
- Use `<style>` for component-specific styles
- Styles are automatically scoped to the component
- Use `:global()` for global styles within component

```astro
<style>
  .container {
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  :global(.global-class) {
    /* Global style */
  }
</style>
```

### Global Styles
- Import global CSS in layouts: `import '../styles/globals.css';`
- Use CSS variables for theming
- Define in `src/styles/globals.css`

